\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\text{damp}}=-b\frac{dy}{dt}
\]

\end_inset

The general solution is given by,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y(t)=Ae^{p_{1}t}+Be^{p_{2}t}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1,2}=-\frac{b}{2m}\pm\sqrt{\frac{b^{2}}{4m^{2}}-\frac{k}{m}}$
\end_inset

